meta.long_description:
# Lithostitched

Lithostitched is a library mod for Fabric and Neoforge with new configurability and compatibility enhancements for worldgen.

## Description

This mod introduces new tools for datapack and modded worldgen developers to utilize, with the aim of increasing inter-project compatibility and expanding configurability in general. Currently, there are features such as:
- Biome modifiers
- Template pool injectors
- Surface rule modifiers
- Guaranteed pieces in jigsaw structures

All of these new capabilities are **data-driven**! Take a look at the [Lithostitched Wiki](https://github.com/Apollounknowndev/lithostitched/wiki) for more information.
